    "Specifically, we added a standard dot-product self-attention layer 61 to calculate the weight of each pixel in the feature map produced by the block3 of ResNet-50.",
    "The attention layer outputs the feature map with the same size as the input feature map to ensure it can be inserted into ResNet-50 seamlessly.",
